summary: This mod adds a Testing Hall like that of Oblivion in Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
New Version : http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12267
This mod adds a Testing Hall like that of Oblivion in Skyrim
There are some rooms where you can find many of the rarer items of Skyrim
For enter to the Testing Hall click \\ and write coc testinghall
For go out click \\ and write coc whiterun
Video Tutorial :
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X_DQuCE-kyQ
author: Rhobar95
